{"tid":49013,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"政府應該立法禁止肥婆進入放題餐廳","createTime":"2016-12-21T11:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T18:25:11.000Z","uid":5713,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c64fa6ac97e3c5e7344dd982472d3c43bc9eb6e7","tid":49013,"uid":5713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T11:54:57.000Z","msg":"岩岩去食韓燒 坐左係度無耐 <br />\n有兩個大肥婆 入左黎坐係我架離 <br />\n一大浸肥婆臭味就唔再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我見撚到佢地四條肥而皺既蓮藕腳真係當堂想嘔出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （未望樣 望到我應得嘔多兩錢重）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n肥婆真係種害人利已既生物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  利用自己醜陋既外形 令到人地食少左 自己就食埋佢地果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以話政府應當盡快立法禁止全港肥婆進入任何自助餐餐廳、放題餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一年慳番黎醫肥婆既醫療費都夠起十條高鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a9a8dedb24380b93f33d2d30a800ed866c68c4","tid":49013,"uid":5713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T11:59:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/21/195754_228fea0f13c3230ad56b1e0122bf2b27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F21%2F195754_228fea0f13c3230ad56b1e0122bf2b27.jpg&h=ec965237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aS9iRfd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaS9iRfd.jpg&h=940c250a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/21/195817_b2049913efde4629aa3ce14a30